item.title: Lab 1 Challenges
item.description: Welcome to the first JayHackers *NIX system competition labs! Password to the next user stored in flag.txt Useful commands: cat, less, more Password to the next user is the home directory of the user Useful commands: pwd, cat, less, more, cd Password to the next user is stored in the file “flag.txt” located in the directory that linux systems store log files (look it up!) Useful commands: pwd, cat, less, more, cd
